row.entry:
Expression that defines the access permissions for target files. Expressions should evaluate to a symbolic or numeric/octal representation of the permissions you want to use.
By default, with no specified expression, files use the default permissions of the destination system.
To use the original source file access permissions, use the following expression: ${record:value('/fileInfo/permissions')}

Record key for creating sequence files. Use one of the
                                        following options:

${record:value(<field path>)}

${uuid()}
